name: Farolappsweb
body:
### Welcome to FarolApp4All Web.
This web application connect with FarolApp4All Api and show the lampposts.
This project is a GUI for FarolApp4All Api.  
Nowadays FarolApp4All only have lampposts of Caceres (Spain) but we obtain more in a future.

FarolApp4All provides:
* Lamppost map
* Light pollution map
* Update a lamppost
* Registry one lamppost

### FarolApp4All Web deployments
Some examples are:  
* [FarolApp4All](http://infra3.dia.fi.upm.es)
